result.name: Princess Men’s Club | Luxury strip club | Gentlemen’s club | Kyiv

reviews.text:
Before going to this club, I read in detail about the reviews and decided to drop in. My experience in brief:
1. Of course, one should be aware of the fact that there is an entry fee and also you simply cannot order a Pepsi and stay there for 2 hours. You need to order as you are enjoying the show.
2. I was there for 5 hours and during my stay not even a single performer bothered me / asked me for extra service / disturbed me for money etc., etc. They accepted money only from those who wanted to reward the performers.
3. Finally, I spoke to one lady and I was genuinely overwhelmed by her nice, polite and humble behavior. In my personal opinion, after a point in time, good manners and behavior are also equally important.
4. So, to conclude, this is indeed a perfect "Gentlemen's Club", literally !

My friend recommend me this strip club in Kiev, and I want to say thank you!!
I attended lots of men’s clubs around the world, and Princess was special. In this place show was held every 40-50 minutes, girls are very gorgeous and kind. This kind of erotic dance was the best here in comparison with another strip clubs.
Also service was perfect - clean and fast! Cocktails very tasty and in good price.
You know, that was absolutely great night, and I will definitely go to Princess Club again very soon ;)

I was here tonight and I consider it as the best strip club in Kiev . Central location , good relations with all employees. Girls are beautiful and are all very active in dancing. They don't force the clients to buy services . Prices are quite normal for Kiev. It's very modern, design, and comfortable with a very good configuration. And a lot of sexy and esthetic performances on a special stage with screen and video effects. Just a beautiful show in a good atmosphere and no scamming . I definitely recommend to visit this place and enjoy the moment. It's a new men's club which deserves to figure on a top list of Kiev best nightlife places to go in to have fun.

I have visited other strip clubs in Kiev such as Scarlett, Rio and so on. This club has much better service. I mean their friendly attitude to guests. For example, they return the change to me when I was paying in cash.  During the lesbian show on the platform, the girl gave me a short dance for free. The service of girls are nice, not only dance but also their attitude.

Only one problem is the dancing room, which is too dark!!!! Only light from a small screen, it causes that I cannot see the body of girls clearly. I would like to watch the body of girls but not a shadow! I hope I can enjoy private dance better next time.

UPDATE FEB 2020: After a disappointing experience last visit in December I visited again and on the club's advice via Instagram, reserved a table. Reserving a table seems to the only way to get a good seat and see all the best action. Dancing (and it is real skilled dancing) on the poles is interspersed by erotic shows and some of these are amazing. The girls are all beautiful in their own way and there will be a lady for every taste in the female form

After multiple visits when in Kiev, I can now say that Princess Club finally gets a well deserved 5 stars. I now understand how it operates and like their approach. The customer is king! Everything you want and hope for from a club in Kiev is available, just a little more discretely offered.. As always and rightly so, the more respect you show a lady the more she will relax with you. Saturday night was one of the best I have experienced from Kiev nightlife.

The club is very well managed and service is quick and professional. The lovely waitresses are constantly looking to see if you need anything but do not intrude. Security is not intimidating. The layout is good and not claustrophobic like smaller clubs and girls rotate round a series of stages so nothing is missed. The music is also recogniseable and enjoyable for my generation, and there was also a live singer on occasion. Drinks can be a little expensive but just be cautious and just choose wisely.
